---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Tools | Kreativ Sound"
  description="Preset Mutator is the current Kreativ Sound browser tool for creating Vital presets from audio, existing presets, or scratch ideas."
  canonical="https://kreativsound.com/tools/"
  activeNav="tools"
>
  <section class="card page-main product-page tools-page">
    <div class="stack">
      <div class="tools-hero tools-hero-grid">
        <div class="tools-hero-copy">
          <p class="product-kicker">Tools lab</p>
          <h1 class="page-title">Preset Mutator</h1>
          <p class="page-lead">A focused browser tool for turning source material into usable Vital preset starting points.</p>
        </div>
        <article class="product-panel product-panel-modern product-panel-accent tools-hero-panel">
          <p class="product-section-kicker">Current direction</p>
          <h2>One product, three creation paths</h2>
          <p>Audio to Preset is the live path. Mutate Preset and From Scratch stay visible as planned modes, but the public promise remains narrow until they are ready.</p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="product-panel-grid product-tool-grid product-tool-grid-single">
        <section class="product-panel product-tool-card product-tool-card-coming-soon product-panel-modern product-panel-accent">
          <span class="product-tool-flow">Audio -&gt; Vital preset</span>
          <img class="product-tool-mark" src="/apps/audio-alchemy/ui/audio-alchemy-mark.svg" width="128" height="128" alt="Preset Mutator logo" />
          <h2>Preset Mutator</h2>
          <p>Upload a short sound and generate guided Vital preset directions in the browser. This is the practical starting point for the full Preset Mutator direction.</p>
          <p class="product-tool-supporting">Best for quick sound-design sketches: pads, plucks, bass notes, drones, and textures that can become playable preset ideas.</p>
          <div class="product-actions">
            <a class="button primary" href="/apps/audio-alchemy/ui/">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-wand-magic-sparkles" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              Open Preset Mutator
            </a>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>

      <section class="product-panel product-panel-summary product-panel-modern">
        <h2>Current tools strategy</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Preset Mutator is the main browser tool product.</li>
          <li>Audio to Preset is the active mode and uses the existing local audio analysis workflow.</li>
          <li>Mutate Preset and From Scratch are planned modes, not separate public products.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="product-panel-grid tools-mode-grid" aria-label="Preset Mutator modes">
        <article class="product-panel product-panel-modern product-panel-accent">
          <p class="product-section-kicker">Live now</p>
          <h2>Audio to Preset</h2>
          <p>Use one short source sound, analyze it locally, and generate Vital preset directions you can refine.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="product-panel product-panel-modern">
          <p class="product-section-kicker">Planned</p>
          <h2>Mutate Preset</h2>
          <p>Load an existing preset and push it into related variations without losing the original sound identity.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="product-panel product-panel-modern">
          <p class="product-section-kicker">Planned</p>
          <h2>From Scratch</h2>
          <p>Generate a new preset direction from a simple intent instead of starting from an audio example.</p>
        </article>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
